  41. "Boxed" state of the "%" button isn't saved on exit.
      [Actually, this is a feature, not a bug. :)  The program does
      not save the state of the settings unless you go into the
      preference editor and save them there.  This allows temporarily
      changing the settings for the current session only.  If this is
      too confusing, or enough users think it should always save the
      current configuration, it's only one line of code I would need
      to add.  I guess I could make it a preference option.]
      [User agreed that it was fine and even a useful feature as is.]
